WEBVTT

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:30.336
I married him

00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:31.816
and left Mumbai,

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:36.016
and went to a small village
which did not have running water

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:37.320
and no toilet.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:42.136
Honestly, my family
and friends were horrified.

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:43.310
(Laughter)

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:46.736
I was staying with my family,

00:01:46.760 --> 00:01:49.376
with my three children in the village,

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.176
and one day,

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:53.456
a few years later one day,

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:56.280
a woman called Kantabai came to me.

00:01:57.480 --> 00:02:02.296
Kantabai said, "I want
